data.description: Welcome to this stunning, low-maintenance townhome built in 2017. This is the higher-end version of these townhomes in this neighborhood. This floor plan offers an open-concept flow, 42-inch cabinets, quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, minutes from the interstate this home offers both style and convenience. Enjoy the resort-style amenities of Durbin Crossing, including pools, tennis courts, basketball courts, volleyball courts, a children's play area, and dog walking parks. Located in the highly sought-after Saint Johns County, this home is zoned for top-rated schools.
